## Epistemic Status

Claims in this paper carry three levels of grounding:

- **Established physics** — bandgap/SEU relationship; thermal conductivity values
- **Physically motivated estimate** — ~2 kg/year yield; solar flux calculations
- **Does not yet exist** — closed orbital supply chain; asteroid ISRU at this scale

-----

## About

The Solbakken Research Initiative is an independent, unaffiliated research program working across photonic AI acceleration, diamond electronics, and orbital manufacturing. This paper is one of several speculative frameworks under active development.

